e":"2020-01-28T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"1ba4f200312de1962c0c737868ff6c1d1969d1c8","tid":1848184,"uid":38795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"陳雲中聯辦間諜認證<br />\n姐係方向正確"},{"pid":"859378f0654865224e3c732411a2d7c3b3638e2b","tid":1848184,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"集民俗學、中醫、自然療法於一身嘅弱智陳雲<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"64de2293cc26073908cc2311480da6e84aba2619","tid":1848184,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"陳雲死全家"},{"pid":"97f4da12d2dfac24a984c61f026447c66b459271","tid":1848184,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"國師又教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d062887338a678877789c9e44d554402b5b67145","tid":1848184,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"國師反對的，我們必須擁護"},{"pid":"56bf9f1cb16e07ba5d987e92b6773de8b7a098b5","tid":1848184,"uid":332304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"冇人想知呢條撚樣講乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫佢返去食屎啦死共諜"},{"pid":"5e99ec656f5980bab132845f92ed79f658f9eb45","tid":1848184,"uid":181655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"共匪陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fbec974e10fdc62eb464a88d1a541f654c5870","tid":1848184,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"4d10fef1c0b5602daede8e9e058d8170196c1cd6","tid":1848184,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡 非常重要！分析文！大力推！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=7aa82dc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡<br />\n整體分析：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=a0495193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n首選：Sellstrom S80225/S80226 Wildland Fire Goggles （戴眼鏡都用得）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Sellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog/dp/B07DJVPL9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog%2Fdp%2FB07DJVPL9Q&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=52023ee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Sellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog/dp/B07DJVPL9Q</a><br />\n<br />\nSellstrom 依款眼罩，上年九月果陣，已經係前線手足標準裝備，有手足認證，包保放心！其中，依款眼罩有兩大特點。<br />\n<br />\n第一，依款眼罩寫明係 non-vented，即係氣密。戴左之後，基本上就阻隔左外面嘅空氣進入眼罩，所以擋到TG，亦都擋到帶病毒嘅飛沫同空氣，乜春都入唔到眼。依個亦都係佢可以俾美國消防員救山火果陣用嘅原因。氣密係眼罩第一重要條件，如果唔係氣密，病毒同TG都可以經眼罩邊位入眼，大陸衛健委都講明病毒傳染性不斷上升，美國有教授都講左武漢沙士嘅reproductive rate 高過曬佢見過佢嘅病毒，證明今次係非常嚴重，必須要用高規格嘅產品保護自己！<br />\n<br />\n第二，依款眼罩經過 ANSI Z87+ 嘅驗證，保護性極高！<br />\nANSI Z87+嘅定義如下：<br />\n&lsquo;Each product must go through rigorous third-party testing which simulates hazards such as impact by flying objects and debris, high mass impact, and sharp object penetration. In each testing scenario, the lenses and frame must stay intact to pass&rsquo;<br />\n根據網上一個對ANSI Z87+ 眼罩嘅測試，散彈槍都射佢唔穿，所以ANSI Z87+ 嘅standard 係非常高，亦都只有依種眼罩嘅保護性先可以保護前線免受橡膠子彈同布袋彈威脅。<br />\n<br />\n但係有巴打指出部份面型有機會有gap, 建議如果屋企多人買多幾種唔同牌子試下<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n次選：<br />\nPyramex CAPSTONE (G504DT或其他型號）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Pyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog/dp/B003UUEW88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog%2Fdp%2FB003UUEW88&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=49f96159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Pyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog/dp/B003UUEW88</a><br />\n<br />\n第一，依款眼罩有氣密帽，應該同樣做到氣密效果，但係因為佢嘅氣密帽可以拆卸，多左個連接位，所以氣密保護性會低小小（始終多個連接位就多個出錯機<br />\n會）。（巴打指出Pyramex Capstone 只係indirect vent，唔係non-vented） <br />\n如果有心改，可以買熱熔膠封透氣孔<br />\n第二，依款眼罩經過D3 測試，證實可以防水滴同化學劑嘅飛淺，理論上有足夠防水性能。<br />\n第三，依款眼罩經過MIL-PRF 32432 美軍標準測試，對子彈衝擊力有一定防禦。<br />\n<br />\n3M 1621 護目鏡<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係完全氣密，但係過左D3 test 同 ANSI Z87.1 （冇過plus 果個），對飛沫有一定預防能力，依幾日試過，除左大霧啲之外其他都ok, 包得幾好，重點係好便，五金舖$20-30 就有，性價比最高！<br />\n巴打指出大霧，唔適合返工<br />\n<br />\n泳鏡（仲易買過平光鏡）<br />\n<br />\n泳鏡顧名思義，就係for 遊水，氣密效果有一定嘅保證，同埋求其一間運動鋪都可以買到，買近視鏡嘅話眼睛都唔洗戴，幾十蚊就有，保護性一定好過平光鏡，不過如果係講嘢都要除口罩，放屁要除褲，戴左帽可能腦都用唔到嘅人，可能佢戴左就會睇唔野。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n8.5 最新護目鏡實測 條帶戴高D 鼻位GAP就會消失!!! &amp; 前線超過400位豬嘴實測<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411916</a><br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手，like &amp; share 等多啲人睇到！<br />\n<br />\n香港眼罩網店列表：（請各位幫手加落去）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3armystore.com/products/pyramex-capstone-dual-lens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3armystore.com%2Fproducts%2Fpyramex-capstone-dual-lens&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=1d09e0d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3armystore.com/products/pyramex-capstone-dual-lens</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.accstoreonline.com/products/sellstrom-wildland-fire-safety-goggles\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accstoreonline.com%2Fproducts%2Fsellstrom-wildland-fire-safety-goggles&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=9a750ed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.accstoreonline.com/products/sellstrom-wildland-fire-safety-goggles</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.autoworld.hk/chinese/pygg504t.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.autoworld.hk%2Fchinese%2Fpygg504t.html&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=a233c671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.autoworld.hk/chinese/pygg504t.html</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=a247b23b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a><br />\n清洗參考<br />\n<br />\n建議清潔步驟<br />\n1.番到屋企，洗手<br />\n2.唔好除眼罩住，用火酒紙清潔眼罩外部<br />\n3.除眼罩口罩，再用酒精/消毒清潔劑/稀釋漂白水清潔成個眼罩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mBGDrY0PyQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmBGDrY0PyQ4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=e93beaf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mBGDrY0PyQ4</a><br />\nSafety test <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=e7df4898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液<br />\n<br />\n#屠龍 #藍絲 #藍屍 #黃色經濟圈 #黃店 #裝備 #口罩 #武漢肺炎 #武漢 #P95 #文宣 #N95 #肺炎 #沙士 #香港 #支那人 #高鐵 #眼罩 #tg #lihkg #連登 #高登 #d100 #黑警"},{"pid":"88efb000603271617a210cd4e784321b0d2545c3","tid":1848184,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3def711837ede2783af3d465412cf2dc1553f4fa","tid":1848184,"uid":63669,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"無興趣知精神病人既廢言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"緊急關頭就睇得出邊個係人邊個係鬼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62828e940510d80003e404f87e13415be3758239","tid":1848184,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"冇留意開佢<br />\n望左望佢D言論精神好似唔太正常<br />\n只係想問下點解大家話佢共諜?"},{"pid":"3f3d70b011587e45d2338ba9eca61213a6f94159","tid":1848184,"uid":38795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62828e940510d80003e404f87e13415be3758239","tid":1848184,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"冇留意開佢<br />\n望左望佢D言論精神好似唔太正常<br />\n只係想問下點解大家話佢共諜?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:51:42.000Z","msg":"每次文匯大公同中共港共屌d咩<br />\n佢同熱狗就會好準時一齊屌，每次都係咁<br />\n所以佢同熱狗好可能係中聯辦派黎分化民主陣營"}]}